title: For Sale:  5.56 NATO SS109 (M855) ZQI BRASS FACTORY AMMO 62 GR.
postcontent:
30rds a box $16 per box.

Brand new, factory fresh SS109 NATO ZQI brand brass case 62 gr ammo. If you are unfamiliar with the brand youtube the great reviews - this has the steel core SS109 bullet, brass case, crimped and sealed boxer primers, and sealed case mouth. Same as M855 but made in Turkey and M855 is the US designation. 

SS109 is the name of the projectile. M855 is the US Military designation for the loaded cartridge (with the SS109 bullet). All ammo loaded to NATO STANAG 4172 spec has an SS109 projectile, including M855. Both SS109 and M855 are included in the potential ban on March 16th.

title: For Sale:  Italian Carcano M41 Rifle
postcontent:
For Sale: Italian Carcano M41 Rifle

From the Armaguerra Cremona arsenal produced from 1942 to 1944. It is numbers matching and complete. There are no markings on the receiver. There are also no import marks anywhere.

It fires the 6.5x52mm Carcano round. It comes with one stripper clip. It prefers the aftermarket ammo compared to the surplus. The bolts on M41 rifles were not new, the Italians used the old bolts from the model 1891 Carcanos to save on production costs and time. While the rifle is over 70 years old, the bolt is over 100 years old.

The stock has been very nicely repaired and restored. The stock was raw and in two pieces when I got it. The Italians imported many in this condition but that is not period correct. To repair the two piece stock I inserted a threaded metal rod into the two pieces and used premium wood glue. However, during the repair the pin on the "lower band spring" snapped. I am looking for a replacement. It does stay in just fine even while it is fired. The hand guard has also been repaired before I owned it, I cleaned the repair up as best as possible. I have more pictures available upon request.

Asking $225 or best offer.

PLEASE NOTE THE FOLLOWING: This is a FTF only deal, must live in Michigan (in a reasonable driving distance), I will not ship (emails asking to ship will be ignored). Serious inquiries only.
